frus:attachment.p:
In addition General Franchet d’Esperey ordered General ChrétienLetter No. 16.099/2M. of July 1.
                                    [Footnote in the original.] to require by July 15, a
                                certain number of guarantees including, among others: 

Suppression of two divisions, one by July 15, the other by
                                        August 1;

Disbanding of the military school at Sofia;

Stopping the filling up again to a full complement in horses
                                        of the cavalry and artillery;

Closing the arms repair factory of the Sofia arsenal.
